Curses companion for hax2 (https://github.com/gmcnutt/hax2) project.

# first install hax2 (https://github.com/gmcnutt/hax2)
# install azoth
$ cd azoth
$ sudo cp tcod/lib/libtcod.so /usr/lib/
$ cd azoth
$ ./azoth.py

Windows: untested, you probably need to use libtcod-mingw.dll from the tcod
download instead of libtcod.so.
